              Project nr. 3
            </h2>

            <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-200 leading-relaxed mb-8">
         
<div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-200 leading-relaxed mb-8">
  <p>
    <strong class="text-[#29cb17]">Fragments of Silence</strong> is a conceptual art project exploring the tension between chaos and stillness in modern digital life. Through layered textures, distorted forms, and muted color palettes, the piece reflects how silence can exist even in overwhelming noise.
  </p>

  <p>
    The work combinesdigital collage, 3D elements, and motion-based experimentatio to create a fragmented visual narrative. Each composition is intentionally imperfect — broken lines, abrupt transitions, and visual glitches are used as a language rather than flaws.
  </p>

  <p>
    The project was developed as an exploration of identity in a hyper-connected world, where constant input often leads to emotional detachment. By stripping away clarity and introducing visual tension, the viewer is invited to pause and interpret the work in their own way.
  </p>
</div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-8">
              <a
                href="/news"
                class="inline-block bg-[#29cb17] hover:bg-lime-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(163,163,163,0.5)] w-fit"
              >
                Read More
              </a>

              <button
                id="showGalleryButton"
                class="inline-block bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-600 hover:border-[#29cb17]"
              >
                See Latest Photos
              </button>
            </div>

            <div id="wweGallery" class="hidden">
              <div class="relative w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
                <div id="wweSlider" class="flex transition-transform duration-500 ease-in-out">
                  <img src="/Billeder/PH.png" class="w-full flex-shrink-0 object-cover rounded-xl h-[350px]" alt="Wrestling 1" />
                  <img src="/Billeder/PH.png" class="w-full flex-shrink-0 object-cover rounded-xl h-[350px]" alt="Wrestling 2" />
                  <img src="/Billeder/PH.png" class="w-full flex-shrink-0 object-cover rounded-xl h-[350px]" alt="Wrestling 3" />
                  <img src="/Billeder/PH.png" class="w-full flex-shrink-0 object-cover rounded-xl h-[350px]" alt="Wrestling 4" />
                  <img src="/Billeder/PH.png" class="w-full flex-shrink-0 object-cover rounded-xl h-[350px]" alt="Wrestling 5" />
                  <img src="/Billeder/PH.png" class="w-full flex-shrink-0 object-cover rounded-xl h-[350px]" alt="Wrestling 6" />
                  <img src="/Billeder/PH.png" class="w-full flex-shrink-0 object-cover rounded-xl h-[350px]" alt="Wrestling 7" />
                  <img src="/Billeder/PH.png" class="w-full flex-shrink-0 object-cover rounded-xl h-[350px]" alt="Wrestling 8" />
                </div>

                <button
                  id="prevSlide"
                  class="absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-black/70 hover:bg-lime-500 text-white px-5 py-3 rounded-full hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 text-xl font-bold"
                >
                  ◀
                </button>

                <button
                  id="nextSlide"
                  class="absolute right-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-black/70 hover:bg-lime-500 text-white px-5 py-3 rounded-full hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 text-xl font-bold"
                >
                  ▶
                </button>

                <div id="slideIndicators" class="absolute bottom-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex gap-2"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <script is:inline>
    const gallery = document.getElementById("wweGallery");
    const button = document.getElementById("showGalleryButton");
    const slider = document.getElementById("wweSlider");
    const next = document.getElementById("nextSlide");
    const prev = document.getElementById("prevSlide");
    const indicators = document.getElementById("slideIndicators");

    if (gallery && button && slider && next && prev && indicators) {
      let index = 0;
      const slides = slider.children.length;

      for (let i = 0; i < slides; i++) {
        const dot = document.createElement("button");
        dot.className = "w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gray-500 hover:bg-lime-500 transition-all duration-300";
        dot.onclick = () => goToSlide(i);
        indicators.appendChild(dot);
      }

      function updateIndicators() {
        Array.from(indicators.children).forEach((dot, i) => {
          dot.className = i === index
            ? "w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-lime-500 scale-125 transition-all duration-300"
            : "w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gray-500 hover:bg-lime-500 transition-all duration-300";
        });
      }

      function goToSlide(n) {
        index = n;
        slider.style.transform = `translateX(-${index * 100}%)`;
        updateIndicators();
      }

      button.addEventListener("click", () => {
        gallery.classList.toggle("hidden");
        button.innerHTML = gallery.classList.contains("hidden")
          ? "📸 See Latest Photos"
          : "✖️ Hide Photos";
      });

      next.addEventListener("click", () => {
        index = (index + 1) % slides;
        goToSlide(index);
      });

      prev.addEventListener("click", () => {
        index = (index - 1 + slides) % slides;
        goToSlide(index);
      });

      updateIndicators();
    }
  </script>
</Layout>